偏导数的符号–指标约定和普通的四矢量是相反的，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\partial_{\mu}=\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t},\nabla\right),\quad\partial^{\mu}=\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t},-\nabla\right),\quad A^{\mu}=\left(\varphi/c,\sbf A\right)
\]

\end_inset

由电动力学：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \nabla\times\sbf E=-\partial_{t}\sbf B=-\partial_{t}\nabla\times\sbf A=\nabla\times\left(-\partial_{t}\sbf A\right)\\
\Rightarrow & \nabla\times\left(\sbf E+\partial_{t}\sbf A\right)=0\\
\Rightarrow & \sbf E=-\nabla\varphi-\partial_{t}\sbf A
\end{align*}

\end_inset

电磁场强张量的定义为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
F^{\mu\nu} & =\partial^{\mu}A^{\nu}-\partial^{\nu}A^{\mu}\\
F^{0i} & =\partial^{0}A^{i}-\partial^{i}A^{0}=\partial^{0}A^{i}+\nabla A^{0}=\partial^{0}\sbf A+\nabla\varphi=-\sbf E
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $A^{\mu}=\left(\varphi/c,\sbf A\right)$
\end_inset

。另一方面，对于磁场：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \sbf B=\nabla\times\sbf A,\quad\varepsilon^{0123}=1,\quad\varepsilon^{123}=1.\\
 & B^{i}=\varepsilon^{ijk}\partial_{j}\left(-A_{k}\right)=-\left(\partial_{j}A_{k}-\partial_{k}A_{j}\right),\\
 & B^{i}\Rightarrow-F_{jk}=-F^{jk},\quad F^{ijk}=-\varepsilon^{ijk}B^{k}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

总结：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{cases}
F^{i0}=E^{i}=\sbf E\\
F^{ij}=-\varepsilon^{ijk}B^{k}
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

写成电磁场强张量：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F^{\mu\nu}=\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
0 & -E^{1} & -E^{2} & -E^{3}\\
E^{1} & 0 & -B^{3} & B^{2}\\
E^{2} & B^{3} & 0 & -B^{1}\\
E^{3} & -B^{2} & B^{1} & 0
\end{array}\right],\quad F^{ab}=\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
0 & -B^{3} & B^{2} & \frac{i}{c}E^{1}\\
B^{3} & 0 & -B^{1} & \frac{i}{c}E^{2}\\
-B^{2} & B^{1} & 0 & \frac{i}{c}E^{3}\\
-\frac{i}{c}E^{1} & -\frac{i}{c}E^{2} & -\frac{i}{c}E^{3} & 0
\end{array}\right]
\]

\end_inset

